#include <bits/stdc++.h>
using namespace std;
#define ll long long int
ll hcf(ll a,ll b)
{
	if(b==0)
		return a;
	return hcf(b,a%b);
}
int main()
{
	int t;
	cin>>t;
	while(t--)
	{
		ll gcd;
		ll n,i,a;
		cin>>n;
		cin>>a;
		gcd=a;
		for(i=1;i<n;i++)
		{
			cin>>a;
			gcd=hcf(gcd,a);
		}
		cout<<gcd<<endl;
	}
	return 0;
}
